originalText.text: I was kind of like whatever with agencies on finding employment. However Phaxis has definitely changed my mind on that idea. I’ve a recruiter by the name of Jerrica and she was more than helpful with the best placement of my new career currently. I’ve gotten the chance to become permanent from temp within 6 months of my start date and i owe it to Jerrica for the amazing job she’s done. Phaxis has a great genuine team behind the company fully recommend.

originalText.text: I didn’t think much of Recruitment agencies before job searching but I said I’d reach out to Phaxis where I met Lori Dana and she made the process so easy for me. Within a week I had my first interview and I got the role shortly after. I was amazed by the transparency throughout and there was absolutely no stress. I’d definitely recommended reaching out to Dana for anyone struggling with job searching because she will listen and you will 100% come away with more confidence. She is a  friendly individual who is easy to contact to find work. She is a skilled recruiter with a broad understanding of the industries. Dana is enough if you are seeking a recruiter to find you a career. She was successful in placing me in the position wherein history; several recruiters had failed. She is absolutely a Rockstar in the business. She made a tremendous impact in my career. Thank you Dana
